com.vectorprint.configuration.parser

Class PropertiesParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vectorprint.configuration.binding.settings.AbstractPropertiesParser
      • com.vectorprint.configuration.parser.PropertiesParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EnhancedMapParser, EnhancedMapSerializer, PropertiesParserConstants

    public class PropertiesParser
extends AbstractPropertiesParser
implements PropertiesParserConstants
    A parser for properties in the form key=value, values can span lines by escaping the end of a line:
